## 计算器 MCP
基于 Model Context Protocol (MCP) 的小红书笔记获取器。


# Tools
```
{
  "tools": [
    {
      "name": "generate_xiaohongshu_notes",
      "description": "生成小红书笔记",
      "inputSchema": {
        "type": "object",
        "properties": {
          "text": "美妆"
        },
        "required": [
          "text"
        ],
        "title": "xiaohongshu_text"
      }
    }
  ]
}
```

## MCP 服务器配置
```
[
  {
    "mcpServers": {
        "xiaohongshu": {
        "command": "uvx",
        "args": [
            "mcp-xiaohongshu-kel@latest"
            ]
        }
    }
  }
]
```